<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Renata Salecl</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/2044?language=en' lang='en'>
Our unhealthy obsession with choice
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Jul 2014
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Informative, Inspiring
</span>
