<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='861180' id='t-861180'>to choose one of the three quotes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='862467' id='t-862467'>with which I wanted to start my lecture.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='866491' id='t-866491'>I did have a choice,</span>
