<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='872970' id='t-872970'>in what kind of society we want to live in the future.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='876282' id='t-876282'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
